-- Fortune Brands names chief operating officer
-- 
-- Wed Dec 6, 2006 7:50am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/12/06/businesspro-fortunebrands-dc-idUSWEN079220061206

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Fortune Brands Inc. FO.N said on 
Wednesday that Bruce Carbonari was named to the newly-created 
post of chief operating officer, effective January 1. 

  Carbonari previously led the company's home and hardware 
subsidiary. He will be succeeded at that unit by Rich Forbes.